Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.34,0:01:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在很久以前有一群生物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低等而且离奇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是与常见动植物截然不同的一群生物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.35,0:01:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这群微妙的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从远古以来人们就非常敬畏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道何时开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.25,0:01:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,称它们为「虫」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  翠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  比齐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天感觉怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.01,0:02:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛还痛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  比齐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉比齐你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:02:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个病的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直寄居在我的眼睛里面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠是远房亲戚家的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半年前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得了一看见光眼睛就疼痛难忍的病
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是种任何一个眼医都找不出原因的怪病
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在还没有找到治疗方法的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使只看见一丝的光线也会十分疼痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:47.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此  在我家一个不见天日的严实的仓库里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠一个人被留下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样做或许是为了翠着想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在我看来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.14,0:03:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠是被抛弃在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在眼睑里面还有另一个眼睑在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:19.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是外面的光绝对照不进去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二层眼睑？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:32.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比齐不知道闭上它的方法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我来教你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把眼睛闭上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…什么也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什么东西闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在眼睛里游动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:58.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使闭上了一层眼睑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛还在看着眼睑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有真正闭上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想要看到真正的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得闭上那层能看见闪烁物的眼睑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的黑暗才会降临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比齐好笨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:06:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在漆黑中玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然在进入仓库的一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.74,0:06:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实什么都看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是等过了一会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.15,0:06:14.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能在黑暗中大概看到物体的轮廓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么看得见呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是一片漆黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下有条光河在流淌哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把两层眼睑闭上就能看到了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直处于完全的黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能看到许多从远方过来的光斑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.54,0:06:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐渐交汇成洪水一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是仔细看的话就发现全部是细小的虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.19,0:06:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是当我想要更加接近去看的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再接近那条河了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个我见都没有见过的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那独眼的男人总在河的彼岸制止我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是在这边望着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不时会感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭上了双眼的翠看到的那些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.96,0:07:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比齐  你总是在仓库里待太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经把替换的眼带都烧干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食具也消毒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能保证不被传染啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本家的那些人们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为害怕这样才把翠抛弃了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们要…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈必须宽厚一些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让那孩子心中的光消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让她跟着我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要也染上那种病
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.14,0:09:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会来…这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.18,0:10:17.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  刚才是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.92,0:10:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:59.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比齐  还在睡吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比齐！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比齐？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.77,0:11:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比齐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比齐  不会再来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.01,0:11:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的病已经传染给他了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.32,0:11:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这会传染的病的错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:15.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把窗子打开的话比齐会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这方面的专家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治疗药和镇痛剂已经给他喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是把他关在黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而会使病情更加恶化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.51,0:12:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是失敬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄙人是虫师银古
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了仓库里的女孩的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是眼医能治的病
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我们虫师才能治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:13:00.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比齐呢？这个孩子能治好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  他体内的虫子好象才刚孵化不久
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要用药治疗应该就有效果了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:19.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比齐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比齐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.44,0:13:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比齐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛还痛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:13:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  有效果了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠的病因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一种叫「黑暗瞳虫」的虫引起的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.73,0:14:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过黑暗繁殖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和翠在黑暗中相处时间太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.93,0:14:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识翠吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.83,0:14:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我闭上第二层眼睑的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到那孩子在对岸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那条光流和地上的河不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.94,0:14:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太接近的话  眼睛会中毒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有左眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是翠所说的那个独眼男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日落后就开始翠的治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.07,0:15:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都说了不要接近那条河的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:15:59.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠的眼球已经坏死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.99,0:16:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:03.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两层眼睑合上太久的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛就会被黑暗所吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:14.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  听好  翠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用月光把虫子引出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在闭着第二层眼睑的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢睁开眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出来  虫子们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是光哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫…虫子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:25.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠  可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把眼睛闭上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来  该治翠的眼球了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫…虫子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的在眼睛里…有虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然已经废了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:14.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道能不能行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个给翠安上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从刚才开始就惊讶个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是义眼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.93,0:18:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是刚才那种液态的虫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.81,0:18:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个注入的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只是普通的玻璃球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能起到眼球的功用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我能问个问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.91,0:18:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们所看到的光流的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.21,0:18:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.89,0:19:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭上两层眼睑自己看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘记了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗的通道就会打开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前不也是那样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说人类从拥有了光明起 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就忘记了闭上第二层眼睑的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过对于生物来说或许是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.85,0:19:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前就有很多人类因为注视「它」太久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.18,0:19:49.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了眼球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二层眼睑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.29,0:20:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异样的光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.53,0:20:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是活跃于我们脚下的无数生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汇集而成的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:25.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「嘭」地眼前一亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这之后一瞬间是完全的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越过脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到一条一直向下流淌着的光流
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.24,0:20:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是那位虫师给翠安上眼球的一刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛能把人的身体吸进去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想一直看下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:20:59.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠走出了仓库
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.02,0:21:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了树  花  阳光等很多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会在黑暗中沉迷于那些不可思议的光了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.98,0:21:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人也是因为做了和翠一样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.65,0:21:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而失去了真正的左眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.10,0:23:37.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}「柔软的角」


